<br>
There are times you Evac by instinct. This is based on years of experience and knowing the capabilities of your group members. A majority of the time I rely on my tank to make the call. ( I am sure that Trakon and Findra of Dark Apotheosis is rather tired of me asking “EVAC????”)<br>
<br>
Yet in the case the healer goes down, and we have 3 mobs on us with no crowd control, I will Evac no questions asked. Just as the Cleric constantly watches the health of the group, I constantly review the battle for a possible Evac.  In the case of raids, I am stricter in the sense that I follow my raid leader commands. <br>
<br>
Yes I have Evaced too early, and sometimes too late. It is an ability that I still am perfecting to this day. Of course as mentioned, it's more the situation that dictates the condition for an Evac. <br>
<br>
BelDaniel<br>
